name: Teia as interpreted by Twitter spaces 3/6
description: While listening to a Teia community talk on Twitter spaces, I discovered that the AI of Twitter still has a lot to learn in order to spell the name Teia correctly in their transcipt. Here is a serie of what Twitter spaces makes of the name Teia. In this case, Teia as Tiatia. Tiatia is a name of a vulcano in Russia. Someone in the community talk said TeiaTeia.
